\int_{x=0}^1 \int_{y=0}^{1-x} \int_{z=0}^{x+y} dz \, dy \, dx =  \int_{z=0}^{1} \int_{x=0}^z \int_{y=z-x}^{1-x}  dy \, dx \,  dz +  \int_{z=0}^{1} \int_{x=z}^1 \int_{y=0}^{1-x}  dy \, dx \,  dz 
